comments: After the ball becomes loose, Sengun (HOU) grabs and pulls Allen's (PHX) arm.
Sengun (HOU) grasps and then quickly releases Durant's (PHX) jersey in the post.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that Thompson's (HOU) shot attempt made contact with the rim and the shot clock is reset to 11 with HOU retaining possession.
VanVleet (HOU) reaches in and the contact with Gordon's (PHX) hand on the ball is incidental.
Bol (PHX) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Bol (PHX) lowers his right arm and initiates illegal contact with Sengun's (HOU) forearm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Durant (PHX) leans slightly to his right and the contact initiated with Sengun (HOU) is marginal.
Brooks (HOU) initiates illegal arm and body contact with Durant (PHX), affecting his driving shot attempt.
Durant (PHX) commits a take foul on Thompson (HOU).
Durant (PHX) brushes Sengun's (HOU) arm during his put-back shot attempt.
Bol (PHX) briefly has an arm around Sengun (HOU) but releases and does not prevent him from getting to the rebound.
Durant (PHX) cleanly blocks Sengun's (HOU) shot attempt at the basket and any further contact is incidental.
Gordon (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Bol (PHX) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Smith Jr.'s (HOU) arm that affects his SQBR.  The illegal contact precedes any possible traveling violation.
Holiday (HOU) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Smith Jr. (HOU).
Smith Jr. (HOU) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
Durant (PHX) fakes his shot attempt during the free throw.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in a legal guarding position in VanVleet's (HOU) path and is dislodged from his position.
Booker (PHX) grabs and pulls Whitmore's (HOU) jersey away from his body, affecting his FOM away from the play.
Allen (PHX) commits a take foul on Sengun (HOU).
